---
title: Tandoori King Prawn Masala Curry with Spinach, Basmati Rice and Crispy Onions
description: This Tandoori King Prawn Masala Curry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
